FBIS3-37731 "drsov036_e_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-036 Document Type:Daily Report 23 Feb 1994 UKRAINE International Affairs Minister Says No Capability To Produce Nuclear Weapons LD2202140394 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 0600 GMT 22 Feb 94 LD2202140394 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service Language: Ukrainian Article Type:BFN [Text] Ukraine's deputy minister of defense, Chief of Armaments of the Ukrainian Armed Forces Colonel-General Ivan Oliynyk met military attaches accredited at foreign embassies in Ukraine. Col-Gen Oliynyk stressed that Ukraine is capable of manufacturing up-to-date arms systems to world standards, except for nuclear ones. He stressed that Ukraine's desire to acquire the non- nuclear state status remains unchanged.
